(455, 1, '2018-06-21 03:59:29', '2018-06-21 03:59:29', '<strong><img class="alignnone wp-image-456 size-full" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-1349x438-1.jpg" alt="" width="1349" height="438" /></strong>\r\n\r\nOcean Edu Việt Nam was established in October 2007. With its seasonable policies, Ocean Edu has developed both in quantities and qualities. At present time, Ocean Edu is running 30 branches with more than 20.000 students studying and other 10.000 students waiting for their classes. Ocean Edu will be hiring Native teachers to teach EFL to young learners in Hanoi, Vietnam and other major cities across North Vietnam. Teaching in Vietnam provides teachers the opportunity to gain teaching experience while living in a fascinating and rapidly emerging country.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Native English Speaker (Britain, Australia, New Zealand and US Citizens are preferred)</li>\r\n 	<li>Must be <strong>24 years old</strong> and <strong>above</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Bachelor’s degree holder</li>\r\n 	<li>With teaching certificates (TESOL, TEFL or CELTA)</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience in ESL/EFL teaching</li>\r\n 	<li>A strong understanding and good command of the English language</li>\r\n 	<li>Enthusiastic, energetic and a natural leader in the classroom</li>\r\n 	<li>Responsible, approachable and friendly</li>\r\n 	<li>Highly organized, detail-oriented and punctual</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>SALARY RANGE:</strong> <strong>$1500 – $1800 USD.</strong>\r\n\r\nEmail your CV/RESUME , Certificates and other relevant materials proving your qualification in teaching English Language.', 'HIRING: FULL TIME NATIVE ENGLISH TEACHER', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hiring-full-time-native-english-teacher', '', '', '2018-06-21 04:17:39', '2018-06-21 04:17:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=455', -1, 'job_listing', '', 0),
